						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab built into the front wall of the deserted Hanumān temple in the old site of the village.</hi></p>						

						<p>Sōmēśvara IV—(Date lost).</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record seems to register a gift of land, oil and income from taxes on betel-leaves to the temple of Mūlasthāna-Bhōgēśvara, by the <hi rend="italic">Mahājanas</hi> and others of <hi rend="bold">Kummaṭage.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
